messages.messageBody:
Hi,

I just wanted to say thank you to whoever posted about
multiflyer.com.

My daughter (who I was told would struggle with math her whole
life), is doing well with this, and absolutely thinks it's fun. She
has been doing awesome with it. I was joking with her, when she was
playing this, and said, I thought math was hard for you, and she
told me it was, until she was playing this. It's not only fun for
multiplication, but also gives some really cool info about the
planets, etc. Yes, I know I said the M word (math), and I know that
you guys probably call it a schooly term, so I'm sorry if I offend
anyone, but for us in this house, it is what it is.

Long story short, thanks to whoever posted about multiflyer.com.
It's alot of fun, and my daughter is learning, and having fun with
math.


HAPPY HALLOWEEN TO EVERYONE!!!!

---Vanessa
